data.description: Welcome to 8854 Bayonne Dr! A stunning 4 bed, 3 bath 2-story home. As you step inside, you're greeted by a spacious open floor plan on the 1st floor, seamlessly connecting the living, dining, & kitchen, creating a warm atmosphere. The 1st floor also hosts the master suite, a versatile space that can be utilized as an in-law suite. This master boasts a separate sitting area, kitchen, private bathroom, & a distinct entry, offering both luxury & privacy. Venture upstairs to find 3 generously sized bedrooms & full bathroom, providing space for family or guests. Step outside into the backyard oasis, where a beautiful in-ground spa pool awaits. This heated pool, equipped with a cleaning system, promises year-round enjoyment! The expansive yard is fully fenced, providing a private space for outdoor activities & gatherings. Near Shreveport's shopping & dining, this home offers both tranquility & accessibility. Don't miss the chance to make this incredible home yours! Schedule a viewing today!
